headline: General Motors (GM): Taking Stock of Valuation After Recent Share Price Momentum
summary: General Motors (GM) shares rose 4% to close at $69.66, building on recent momentum in the US auto sector. Over the past month, the stock has gained 14%, a reflection of investor interest during a quieter news period. See our latest analysis for General Motors. GM’s latest rally caps off a robust year for shareholders, with a total return of 35% over the past year and an impressive 109% over five years.
